data.description: Inviting 3-bed, 2-bath home in a tranquil gated community with various upgrades. Demonstrating pride of ownership, it features new windows, sun screens, a 2021 roof, and custom front and sliding glass doors. Exterior lighting is updated, and attic insulation recently added. Inside, discover new appliances, new countertops, and a farmhouse sink in the kitchen. The 2023 flooring update extends throughout, while both bathrooms boast new countertops and toilets, with the primary bathroom showcasing a new shower enclosure. All bedrooms feature updated light fixtures. This move-in-ready gem offers a perfect blend of comfort and style!
